SM LOCALES
----------

This module/package will contain all the strings needed for SM 
internationalization.

Releases will deal with SM packages compatibility. Having in its version
numbering enough tips to know if it's compatible with a specific SM release.

Translation files:
help/ - directory holds all help system translations
install - script is used to install squirrelmail translations. It is added
          in every package.
locale/ - directory holds all gettext translations.
version - file used to track translation version.
independent_strings.txt - extra strings that can't be extracted from squirrelmail
                          php files.

Support scripts:
compilepo      - script compiles locales. It uses locale name as first argument.
mergepo        - script combines strings in main squirrelmail.po with translation
                 strings. It uses translation name as first argument.
buildpackages  - script compiles and builds separate translation packages in 
                 packages/ directory.
compilelocales - script compiles all squirrelmail.mo files
status         - script generates html page with status of translations
